            "text_tTczpt": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p><strong>FourFour comes from a family that has made belts for over 30 years</strong>. We know the craft, the materials, the supply chain — all of it, from the inside. <br/>And when we looked at what modern material science had made possible, we made a choice: there is no reason luxury needs a victim anymore.<br/><strong>Not a compromise. Not a cause. A better product.<br/></strong><br/><strong>Our vegan leather is engineered to outlast & outperform the conventional alternative</strong>. The construction behind every FourFour belt carries three decades of manufacturing knowledge — the kind that doesn’t come from a catalogue or a dropship link.<br/>We didn’t build this brand to make you feel guilty about what’s in your wardrobe.<br/>We built it because desire doesn’t need a victim — and we wanted to prove it.<br/><br/><strong>Luxury can be kind</strong>. That’s not a tagline. It’s the whole point.</p><p><br/></p>",
